  <description type="morphology">Herbs, loosely matted, 0.5–2.5(–3) × 1–3(–5) dm, tomentose or glabrous. Leaves: blade oblanceolate to elliptic, 0.5–1(–1.2) × 0.2–0.4(–0.5) cm. Inflorescences virgate or cymose; branches dichotomous, mostly slender. Involucres 1.5–4 mm. Flowers 2–3 mm; perianth white to pink. Achenes 2–2.5 mm. 2n = 34.</description>
